{"tid":1399514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個港豬上司好撚辛苦....","createTime":"2019-08-03T07:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:36:44.000Z","uid":58841,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8705898cd017fb126310403486976fb4fa46acb4","tid":1399514,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:48:19.000Z","msg":"話咩塞地鐵阻人返工就係唔岩<br />\n好搞唔搞搞著人地搵食<br />\n話後生有份收錢搞事<br />\n我同佢講我屋企人就係前線親眼見到佢地用自己份人工去買物資都唔撚信<br />\n仲話睇唔起我屋企人<br />\n見一個客講一次聽日將軍澳會好亂留返係屋企唔好出黎<br />\n已經好忍住唔開佢地波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係除左佢其他同事都係黃絲 有份出黎發夢<br />\n原來對住差唔多兩年既上司係咁撚....<br />\n好撚想死...."},{"pid":"846998e36e7939f3e271a4f0e0cdd5142eaef905","tid":1399514,"uid":58841,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"已經潛規則唔同客人講政治野<br />\n你逼鳩人地附和你想點撚樣"},{"pid":"59bf081035ce7e5d1fc925eadb96c6e08ee9feec","tid":1399514,"uid":135798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"無腦都可以做到上司 ？"},{"pid":"571b474ef746878d0c71fe85d864edd9e8046d3e","tid":1399514,"uid":43959,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"59bf081035ce7e5d1fc925eadb96c6e08ee9feec","tid":1399514,"uid":135798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"無腦都可以做到上司 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:51:32.000Z","msg":"無腦做特首都得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf23e77fbc099d29e37d9a9e36a4a9ea5827c5b","tid":1399514,"uid":41613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話抗爭者係垃圾，好撚想大巴車落條8婆到"},{"pid":"b4c8f61b1d20a1c800880c546d562504d6bc9662","tid":1399514,"uid":108199,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T07:52:53.000Z","msg":"工作避談政治<br />\n有咩放上黎或tg就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a9335